	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss1":"<???>Get away!",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player1":"<You>Who is there？",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss2":"<???>Get out...Stop getting nearer.",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player2":"<You>Why？Who are you？",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss3":"<???>...",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss4":"<???>Then I have to teach you a lesson.",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss5":"<???>Sure enough，it's deserved to be...",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss6":"<???>It seems that I still lost this time.",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player3":"<You>Who the hell are you？",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss7":"<???>It doesn't hurt to tell you now.",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss8":"<???>I'm the guardian of the dream tower. I've been protecting something for many years.",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player4":"<You>What are you protecting？",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss9":"<???>It's already in your hands now...",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss10":"<???>You must have got what you want now.",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player5":"<You>Me？I didn't want anything,and what do I get？",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss11":"<???>Well, it's a good thing you don't know“",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player6":"<You>...?",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss12":"<???>You have destroyed my image, and now I won't stay in the world for long.",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss13":"<???>Remember,do not use what you haved got to create anything.",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player7":"<You>Wait，I can't understand，why...",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.boss14":"<???>Good luck",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player8":"<You>What the...",
	"dream.word.dream_tower.boss.player9":"<You>Um...",

    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player1":"<You>Here is？",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine1":"<Old Man>The edge of dream,",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine2":"<Old Man>a place you will arrive at when your dream broke.",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player2":"<You>My dream broke？",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine3":"<Old Man>You defeat the nightmare ,don't you？",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player3":"<You>How do you know that？",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine4":"<Old Man>...I felt its dying out。This feeling, is the same as before",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine5":"<Old Man>I have also been rippling in the dream ocean and immersing in the illusion",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine6":"<Old Man>I also used to be the pioneer,connecting dream and reality",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine7":"<Old Man>I also saved the world with the material in the dream",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine8":"<Old Man>Although, it's only temporary",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player4":"<You>You are...",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine9":"<Old Man>Nightmares are originated from people's greed",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine10":"<Old Man>People's unlimited demands on dream eventually lead to its revenge",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine11":"<Old Man>The revenge is disposable,also devastating",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine12":"<Old Man>You must have done something you can't just like them,right?",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player5":"<You>Um...",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine13":"<Old Man>It's all right. People are the same. Everyone will make mistake",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player6":"<You>Is there other people in the world？",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine14":"<Old Man> To these questions,You have to find answers on your own",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine15":"<Old Man>...What I can tell is,just thinking,keeping thinking when you back.",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine16":"<Old Man>The more you think,the more you wikk know",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player7":"<You>Back...Back to where？",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine17":"<Old Man>Where you come from",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player8":"<You>Where I come from......is gone",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player9":"<You>It was I who destroyed the world",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player10":"<You>...",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine18":"<Old Man>I can separate dimensions again, just as I have done before",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player11":"<You>As you have done before",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine19":"<Old Man>As I said, I have briefly extended the life of the world",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player12":"<You>That's means,the world had been destoryed...But before I came to my dream, wasn't the world still complete？",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player13":"<You>Do you,come from another world？",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine20":"<Old Man>......",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player14":"<You>You want to tell me something,but you just can't tell it out,right?",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine21":"<Old Man>......",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine22":"<Old Man>I can only help you here",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine23":"<Old Man>The next road is up to you to choose",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player15":"<You>But I want to know more!",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player16":"<You>Where I come from!The other people in the world!And......",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Player17":"<You>your world......",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine24":"<Old Man>I said,you should think more on you own",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine25":"<Old Man>It's getting late",
    "dream.word.the_edge_cabin.Marine26":"<Old Man>Wake up,my friend",
        
